headline: AT&T Stock Is Back to Multiyear Highs. Time to Buy?
summary: AT&T (NYSE: T) stock appears to be benefiting from its most promising outlook in years.  Admittedly, AT&T gave investors little to like in recent years.  In contrast, Verizon and T-Mobile grew through their single-minded focus on their communications networks.
